  (* Then *)
  Have: i_1 < n.
  If a_11 = 1
  Then {
    Have: (rear_3 = rear_5) /\ (a_10 = Mint_1).
    If Mint_1[a_12] = 0
    Then {
      Have: rear_5 = rear_2.
      If rear_2 < n
      Then {
        Let x_7 = 1 + rear_1.
        Let m = Mint_1[shift_sint32(queue_0, x_7) <- i_1][a_12 <- 1].
        Have: rear_2 = rear_1.
        Have: x_7 = rear_0.
        Have: m[shift_sint32(dist_0, i_1) <- 1 + m[a_9]] = Mint_0.

  (* Then *)
  Have: i_1 < n.
  If a_11 = 1
  Then {
    Have: (rear_3 = rear_5) /\ (a_10 = Mint_1).
    If Mint_1[a_12] = 0
    Then {
      Have: rear_5 = rear_2.
      If rear_2 < n
      Then {
        Let x_7 = 1 + rear_1.
        Let m = Mint_1[shift_sint32(queue_0, x_7) <- i_1][a_12 <- 1].
        Have: rear_2 = rear_1.
        Have: x_7 = rear_0.
        Have: m[shift_sint32(dist_0, i_1) <- 1 + m[a_7]] = Mint_0.
      }
      Else { Have: (Mint_1 = Mint_0) /\ (rear_2 = rear_0). }
    }
    Else { Have: (Mint_1 = Mint_0) /\ (rear_5 = rear_0). }
  }
  Else { Have: (rear_3 = rear_0) /\ (a_10 = Mint_0). }
  (* Invariant 'i_12' *)

  (* Then *)
  Have: i_1 < n.
  If a_8 = 1
  Then {
    Have: (rear_3 = rear_5) /\ (a_4 = Mint_1).
    If Mint_1[a_9] = 0
    Then {
      Have: rear_5 = rear_2.
      If rear_2 < n
      Then {
        Let x_3 = 1 + rear_1.
        Let m = Mint_1[shift_sint32(queue_0, x_3) <- i_1][a_9 <- 1].
        Have: rear_2 = rear_1.
        Have: x_3 = rear_0.

      Else { Have: (Mint_1 = Mint_0) /\ (rear_2 = rear_0). }
    }
    Else { Have: (Mint_1 = Mint_0) /\ (rear_5 = rear_0). }
  }
  Else { Have: (rear_3 = rear_0) /\ (a_4 = Mint_0). }
  (* Invariant 'i_12' *)
  Have: (-1) <= i_1.
  (* Invariant 'i_16' *)

  (* Invariant 'i_21' *)

  (* Invariant 'i_22' *)

  (* Invariant 'i_23' *)

      ((Mint_0[shift_sint32(dist_0, i_2)] != (-1)) -> ((0 <= i_2) ->

  (* Then *)
  Have: i_1 < n.
  If a_9 = 1
  Then {
    Have: (rear_3 = rear_5) /\ (a_8 = Mint_1).
    If Mint_1[a_10] = 0
    Then {
      Have: rear_5 = rear_2.
      If rear_2 < n
      Then {
        Let x_5 = 1 + rear_1.
        Let m = Mint_1[shift_sint32(queue_0, x_5) <- i_1][a_10 <- 1].
        Have: rear_2 = rear_1.
        Have: x_5 = rear_0.
        Have: m[shift_sint32(dist_0, i_1) <- 1 + m[a_7]] = Mint_0.

    }
    Else { Have: (Mint_1 = Mint_0) /\ (rear_5 = rear_0). }
  }
  Else { Have: (rear_3 = rear_0) /\ (a_8 = Mint_0). }
  (* Invariant 'i_12' *)
  Have: (-1) <= i_1.
  (* Invariant 'i_16' *)
  Have: forall i_2 : Z. ((Mint_0[shift_sint32(dist_0, i_2)] != (-1)) ->

  Else { Have: (rear_3 = rear_0) /\ (a_8 = Mint_0). }
  (* Invariant 'i_12' *)

  Else { Have: (rear_3 = rear_0) /\ (a_8 = Mint_0). }
  (* Invariant 'i_12' *)
